FILE STRUCTURE
==============

## Entry points

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| main.tsx | App entry point — mounts React into the DOM |
| App.tsx | Root component — renders AppShell and wires top-level routing between pages |

---

## store/

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| useEditorStore.ts | Central Zustand store — owns all app state (SD card handle, loaded models, radio config, settings, dirty flags) and all async actions (load, save, backup, delete) |

---

## fs/ — SD card & file I/O

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| sdcard.ts | Low-level File System Access API wrapper — open SD card, read/write/delete files, list directories |
| backup.ts | Backup logic — write timestamped YAML copies to BACKUP/, prune oldest beyond the limit |
| webconfig.ts | Persists app settings (e.g. backupCount) to a JSON file on the SD card between sessions |
| download.ts | Triggers a browser download of a YAML file (for export without SD card) |

---

## codec/ — YAML parsing & serialisation

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| model-codec.ts | Parse/serialise model YAML files to/from the Model TypeScript type |
| radio-codec.ts | Parse/serialise the radio-level radio.yml to/from the Radio type |
| modelTemplate.ts | Generates a blank Model with sensible defaults for new model creation |
| modelSummary.ts | Derives a human-readable summary string from a model (shown on model cards) |
| yaml-io.ts | Shared YAML parse/stringify helpers (wraps the js-yaml library) |
| logicalSwDef.ts | Definitions and labels for logical switch function types |
| protocols.ts | RC protocol definitions (SBUS, CRSF, etc.) and their channel counts |
| srcRaw.ts | Source input mappings (sticks, switches, pots) used in mixes |
| switches.ts | Switch definitions — names, positions, and which physical switches exist on the MT12 |

---

## types/ — TypeScript types

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| model.ts | Model type — full structure of a model config (mixes, limits, flight modes, timers, etc.) |
| radio.ts | Radio type — radio-global settings structure |
| fsa.d.ts | Type declarations for the File System Access API (browser API not yet in all TS libs) |
| css-modules.d.ts | Tells TypeScript that *.module.css imports are valid |

---

## data/

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| vehicleTypes.ts | Built-in vehicle category definitions (car, crawler, boat, etc.) with default channel assignments |

---

## pages/ — top-level views

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| ModelList.tsx | Main screen — grid of all model cards on the SD card, new/import/delete actions |
| ModelEditor.tsx | Model editing screen — tab bar + renders the active editor tab for a loaded model |
| RadioSettings.tsx | Radio-global settings editor (trainer port, audio, etc.) |
| VehicleTypesPage.tsx | Manage custom vehicle type categories |

---

## components/layout/ — chrome

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| AppShell.tsx | Outer shell — SD card connect button, nav, modals overlay |
| TabBar.tsx | Tab navigation within ModelEditor |
| SettingsModal.tsx | Settings dialog (backup count, etc.) |
| AboutModal.tsx | About/version dialog |

---

## components/models/ — model list UI

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| ModelCard.tsx | Single card in the model grid — thumbnail, name, summary, actions |
| ModelSummary.tsx | Renders the text summary line on a card |
| BackupHistory.tsx | Dropdown/panel showing previous backups for a model with restore action |

---

## components/mixes/ — mix editor

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| MixEditor.tsx | Container for all mix channels |
| ChannelGroup.tsx | Groups mix lines by output channel |
| MixLine.tsx | Single mix line row (source, weight, switch, etc.) |
| MixLineModal.tsx | Full detail edit modal for a single mix line |
| BasicMixView.tsx | Simplified "basic" view of mixes for less advanced users |
| basicPatterns.ts | Pattern matching to detect if a mix fits a "basic" shape |
| mixProse.ts | Generates plain-English descriptions of mix lines |

---

## components/ — other editors (one per model tab)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| limits/LimitsEditor.tsx | Channel limits (min/max/centre/reverse/subtrim) |
| expos/ExpoEditor.tsx | Expo & rate curves per flight mode |
| flightmodes/FlightModeEditor.tsx | Flight mode names and switch assignments |
| logicalsw/LogicalSwEditor.tsx | Logical switch conditions (AND/OR/comparisons) |
| specialfn/SpecialFnEditor.tsx | Special functions (e.g. play sound on switch) |
| timers/TimerEditor.tsx | Model timers configuration |
| module/ModuleEditor.tsx | RF module and receiver binding settings |
| radio/Mt12Diagram.tsx | SVG diagram of the MT12 transmitter, highlights active controls |
| kidmode/KidModeWizard.tsx | Wizard to generate a rate-limited model config for kids |
| kidmode/kidGenerator.ts | Logic that builds the kid-mode model from wizard answers |
| kidmode/kidDefaults.ts | Default values used by the kid mode generator |

---

## components/shared/ — reusable widgets

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| SrcRawPicker.tsx | Dropdown for picking a mix source input |
| SwitchPicker.tsx | Dropdown for picking a switch |
| WeightSlider.tsx | Slider for mix weight / percentage values |
| FlightModeCheckboxes.tsx | Checkbox grid for enabling something per flight mode |
| DirtyBadge.tsx | Small indicator shown when a model has unsaved changes |
| Tooltip.tsx | Generic tooltip wrapper |

---

## tests/

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| codec/round-trip.test.ts | Parses fixture YAMLs and re-serialises them, asserts output matches input |
| codec/flightModes.test.ts | Flight mode parse/serialise edge cases |
| codec/logicalSwDef.test.ts | Logical switch definition parsing |
| codec/destCh.test.ts | Destination channel mapping |
| codec/subType.test.ts | Protocol sub-type handling |
| kidmode/generator.test.ts | Kid mode generator output assertions |
| fixtures/*.yml | Real MT12 YAML files used as test inputs |
